data.description: Welcome to your dream home located in the highly acclaimed Katy ISD. This lovely 4 bedroom, 3.5 bath residence spans two stories of tastefully designed living space. The main floor boasts a spacious layout that seamlessly connects the living, breakfast, and kitchen areas, creating the ideal space for both entertaining and everyday living. The kitchen features stainless appliances and gas cooktop for the chef (refrigerator will stay). On the upper level, a generous game room awaits, complete with built-in granite-top desk, perfect for work, study, or hobbies. One of the upstairs bedrooms is a versatile suite with its own ensuite bath. The primary bedroom suite is a true retreat, featuring an ensuite bathroom with a separate tub and shower, complete with a comfortable seat. Step outside to discover not one, but two covered patios to enjoy. Don't miss out on this incredible chance to make this beautiful house your new home. Transferrable Home Warranty coverage thru 3/30/2025!
